message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you this incredible opportunity to acquire this valuable product. I believe it's a game-changer for your business and I'm willing to make a deal that will benefit both of us. I'm offering the product to you for $900,000. This is a competitive price considering the product's worth to you is $1,000,000. I'm confident you'll see the value in this investment and I'm looking forward to hearing back from you.
